<span id="freeTextContainer1308244322199237370">A good story. I am surprised it was a &apos;best seller&apos; because the characters lacked depth, and the narrative lacked suspense, in my opinion. Although an attempt was made but didn&apos;t quite come to fruition. I will say I expected more from the book seeing how popular it was. Then again, it did have its moments. The story itself was interesting, and the reason I finished. It did take a little bit of encouragement, though. Usually, I would have read the book much faster, but I struggled with this one. </span>
  <span id="freeText1308244322199237370" style="display:none">A good story. I am surprised it was a 'best seller' because the characters lacked depth, and the narrative lacked suspense, in my opinion. Although an attempt was made but didn't quite come to fruition. I will say I expected more from the book seeing how popular it was. Then again, it did have its moments. The story itself was interesting, and the reason I finished. It did take a little bit of encouragement, though. Usually, I would have read the book much faster, but I struggled with this one. Of course, everyone has different tastes and opinions, and this is mine, 'A narrative that had a real chance but fell flat.'<br /><br />Sorry, all!</span>
